x4freetext: Target thickness corresponded to the energy loss of
2.5 keV for the protons with the energy of 3 MeV.
Uncertainties in the definition of relative cross
section including the statistical errors were 6% for
proton energies of 1500- 1800 keV and 3% for the lager
energies.

x4freetext: Isotope targets were prepared directly in the
electromagnetic separator by beating of the 36Ar ions
into beryllium backings. Argon of natural isotopic
composition was used for target preparation. Targets
manufactured from unenriched gas contained
approximately 25% of 40Ar.
